products.description: Ideal for consoles, gaming laptops and mini PCs, FireCuda SATA SSHD hard drives feature SSD performance and HDD capacities. Enjoy 7200 RPM speeds for a faster, seamless gaming experience—from loading maps for booting levels. Choose from a variety of speeds and cache for an optimized rig and enjoy low power consumption for a more cost effective setup. They even come with a five year limited warranty for long term peace of mind. Combining flash technology with a hard drive platform, the FireCuda 2.5 flash accelerated hard drive represents the fastest 2.5 inch hard drive available.The FastestPC Hard Drive. Best Fit Applications :Mainstream PCs upgrade,High performance PCs, PC gaming systems, Workstations, Creative professional systems.
